Former deputy minister of finance Sfiso Buthelezi is suing former ANC MP Mabel "Vytjie" Mentor for allegedly trying to break up his marriage. This after Mentor took to social media and allegedly accused him of cheating on his wife with a married medical doctor. She also allegedly accused him of buying his nyatsi a property overseas using funds from the Public Investment Corporation (PIC). TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD  